{"tid":338483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得月台啲人成日迫入嚟車廂好撚on9？","createTime":"2017-07-28T08:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T17:31:59.000Z","uid":49312,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec501cc2f5bc1dfcee7028183a8f54c009e83948","tid":338483,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:37:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚覺呀仆街</span></span><br />\n你哋班閪佬個撚個塞撚住晒<br />\n圍撚住條柱 頂撚住晒去唔到對面度門<br />\n又硬係要企係櫈隔離 單檔後面成村人入唔到去車廂中間<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/163453_e2c17841709470724713aaae0d942576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F163453_e2c17841709470724713aaae0d942576.jpg&h=8ea990a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑色就係個啲仆街啦<br />\n<br />\n又就嚟收工啦 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行入去啦屌你老味</span>"},{"pid":"9cc258bec1ecb8a739c22237cbe98b4bb8d1c380","tid":338483,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"行返入去啦屌你老母！"},{"pid":"23fcf6811d54dd5218da05afeeeabb63c627e3d6","tid":338483,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:40:16.000Z","msg":"企係度 門又閂唔到 車又開唔到"},{"pid":"e90461ce2a5662cc22887e502f9b26b3ff6b1825","tid":338483,"uid":87732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:43:57.000Z","msg":"塞撚住晒啲位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96e0bafb93959c0406fc7b778906c1ae6923deb","tid":338483,"uid":118623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T08:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/8d/Transport30.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20090101130636\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i