既人<br />\n都未落你班撚樣就爭住上</blockquote><br />\n萬里長城咁樣企晒係度"},{"pid":"b76ecc6d75b0661de8f06106670198e4f4611186","tid":338483,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"好多掛住睇電話"},{"pid":"aee55300dd53c9ec647fb65e23fd3b3da0afa559","tid":338483,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>塞住d位唔比咁多人入先正常,等過第2架唔得咩,見倒入面咁迫仲夾硬塞入黎要大家陪你一齊迫=on9</blockquote><br />\n問題係入面唔迫呀嘛 睇圖先</blockquote><br />\n我講緊迫果陣,所以我多數入去之後霸住門口角位,試過比人搶咗先,跟住成程車連扶手都無得扶,比人迫到含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n疊羅漢咁呀嘛"},{"pid":"65af6c4a77dbd29186496ddbc537bef3fb943ab3","tid":338483,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工已經趕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要格硬迫入嚟 搞到道門不斷開 阻撚住曬</blockquote><br />\n行入啲咪得囉"},{"pid":"ca40168f3f443ff360b7488598838c6cb3f1d7e8","tid":338483,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T10:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有啲唔撚比人落車既人<br />\n都未落你班撚樣就爭住上</blockquote><br />\n萬里長城咁樣企晒係度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最鐘意落車果陣企係啲係咁迫入黎既人面前<br />\n等佢入唔到，要比人落左先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8534b1b4cbf7a24c006e0ba2c6f5a6549fbb1c9e","tid":338483,"uid":49508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"左右門中間整條柱呢個設計本身就係製造擠塞<br />\n學日本冇柱啦"},{"pid":"356f1600b7b1e55838e05f5d4e4dfaf630d2ff5c","tid":338483,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"開聲屌鳩佢囉"}]}